00:00:11.646 --> 00:00:15.686
For this project, you'll need
a black light, some brushes,

00:00:15.686 --> 00:00:19.400
some spoons, one half
cup of corn starch,

00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:23.330
some food coloring, and one
half cup of highlighter water.

00:00:23.330 --> 00:00:26.300
You're probably asking, how
do you make highlighter water?

00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:28.515
Well, we're gonna
show you right now.

00:00:28.515 --> 00:00:30.340
