highlighter water, you

00:00:30.340 --> 00:00:33.150
need to remove the ink
tube from the highlighter.

00:00:33.150 --> 00:00:35.440
Make sure an adult
helps you with this one.

00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:38.515
Then, you're gonna run the ink
tube through water into a cup

00:00:38.515 --> 00:00:40.430
and squeeze all the ink through.

00:00:40.430 --> 00:00:42.940
And that's how you make
your highlighter water.

00:00:42.940 --> 00:00:45.710
Just mix it after,
and it'll be nice.

00:00:45.710 --> 00:00:48.390
Now, mix your highlighter
water into the corn starch.

00:00:48.390 --> 00:00:49.100
Be careful.

00:00:49.100 --> 00:00:50.068
This can get messy.

00:01:03.150 --> 00:01:04.060
Now, mix it all up.

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:10.192
Now, you can add a
few drops of food

00:01:10.192 --> 00:01:11.900
coloring if you want
to change the color.

00:01:36.550 --> 00:01:37.536
All done.

00:01:37.536 --> 00:01:39.820
